legend bottom
    |= Step |= What Happens |= UNIX Equivalent |= Pattern |= SOLID |
    | 1 | Client calls FileSearchService.search() | find command | Facade | SRP, DIP |
    | 2 | File, Directory, SymLink share base class | inodes | Composite (FS tree) | LSP |
    | 3 | Local / InMemory / Remote file system | local vs NFS | Strategy | DIP, OCP |
    | 4 | Filter interface: apply(entry) -> boolean | predicate | Strategy (core) | ISP, OCP |
    | 5 | Name, Size, Type, Date, Owner, Content filters | -name, -size, -type, -mtime, -user | Strategy | SRP, OCP |
    | 6 | And / Or / Not compose any filters | -a / -o / ! | Composite (filter tree) | OCP, LSP |
    | 7 | DFS / BFS / Parallel traversal + Visitor | tree walk | Strategy + Visitor | OCP, SRP |
    | 8 | Fluent builder for search params | find flags | Builder | SRP |
    | 9 | Sort by name/size/date, SearchResult with metadata | sort, head | Strategy | OCP |
endlegend

